## API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Public |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Public |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Authenticated |

### Borrower
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| POST | `/api/borrower/application/personal` | Borrower |
| POST | `/api/borrower/application/upload` | Borrower |
| GET | `/api/borrower/application` | Borrower |
| POST | `/api/borrower/loans` | Borrower |
| GET | `/api/borrower/loans/my` | Borrower |

### Executive (Dashboard)
| Method | Endpoint | Access |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/executive/leads` | Admin, Sales |
| GET | `/api/executive/loans?status=applied` | All executives |
| PATCH | `/api/executive/loans/:id/sanction` | Admin, Sanction |
| PATCH | `/api/executive/loans/:id/disburse` | Admin, Disbursement |
| POST | `/api/executive/loans/:id/payment` | Admin, Collection |
| GET | `/api/executive/loans/:id/payments` | All executives |

---

## Business Rules (BRE)

The eligibility check runs **on the server** (cannot be bypassed):

| Rule | Condition |
|------|-----------|
| Age | Must be between 23 and 50 years |
| Monthly Salary | Minimum ₹25,000 |
| PAN Format | Must match `[A-Z]{5}[0-9]{4}[A-Z]{1}` (e.g. ABCDE1234F) |
| Employment | Must not be Unemployed |

## Loan Interest Formula

```
Simple Interest (SI) = (P × R × T) / (365 × 100)

Where:
  P = Principal amount (₹50,000 – ₹5,00,000)
  R = 12 (fixed 12% p.a.)
  T = Tenure in days (30 – 365)

Total Repayment = P + SI
```

## Loan Status Flow

```
APPLIED → SANCTIONED → DISBURSED → CLOSED
              ↓
           REJECTED
```

- **Applied** → Borrower submits loan
- **Sanctioned** → Sanction exec approves
- **Rejected** → Sanction exec rejects (with reason)
- **Disbursed** → Disbursement exec releases funds
- **Closed** → Auto-closed when total paid ≥ total repayment

